{
  "texts": [
    "Topic Distance.",
    "We repeat this analysis, but this time aggregating entities at the event/label level, using the 'Topic' split results.",
    "The model specification is left as above, with the introduction of a single additional variable: the minimum cosine distance to any event in the training set.",
    "The coefficients are provided in Table E.3.",
    "While comparison across Tables E.2 and E.3 is not directly possible, as each estimates using different entities and different models, it is encouraging to see similar magnitudes for most variables' coefficients."
  ]
}